'''反羽蟹科'''（[[學名|學名]]：{{lang|la|'''Retroplumidae'''}}）是'''幽靈蟹總科'''（'''Retroplumoidea'''）下唯一的[[單系群|單系]][[科|科]]。

== 分類 ==
反羽蟹科下有8個[[屬|屬]]，但只有Bathypluma及反羽蟹屬兩個屬有發現現存物種：<ref name="Grave">{{cite journal |journal=[[Raffles_Bulletin_of_Zoology|Raffles Bulletin of Zoology]] |year=2009 |volume=Suppl. 21 |pages=1–109 |title=A classification of living and fossil genera of decapod crustaceans |author=Sammy De Grave, N. Dean Pentcheff, Shane T. Ahyong ''et al.'' |url=http://rmbr.nus.edu.sg/rbz/biblio/s21/s21rbz1-109.pdf |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110606064728/http://rmbr.nus.edu.sg/rbz/biblio/s21/s21rbz1-109.pdf |archivedate=2011-06-06 |access-date=2013-04-19 }}</ref>
*''Archaeopus'' † <small>Rathbun, 1908</small>
*[[深海羽蟹属|深海羽蟹属]] ''Bathypluma'' <small>de Saint Laurent, 1989</small>
*[[闭羽蟹属|闭羽蟹属]] ''Costacopluma'' † <small>Collins & Morris, 1975</small>
*[[克里斯蒂羽蟹属|克里斯蒂羽蟹属]] ''Cristipluma'' † <small>Bishop, 1983a</small>
*''Loerentheya'' † <small>Lőrenthey, in Lőrenthey & Beurlen, 1929</small>
*''Loerenthopluma'' † <small>Beschin, Busulini, De Angeli & Tessier, 1996</small>
*[[反足蟹属|反足蟹属]] ''Retrocypoda'' † <small>Vía, 1959</small>
*[[反羽蟹屬|反羽蟹屬]]（''Retropluma''） <small>Gill, 1894</small>

這兩個屬合共十個品種，生活於[[印度洋-太平洋海域|印度洋-太平洋海域]]<ref>{{cite journal |journal=[[Raffles_Bulletin_of_Zoology|Raffles Bulletin of Zoology]] |year=2008 |volume=17 |pages=1–286 |title=Systema Brachyurorum: Part I. An annotated checklist of extant Brachyuran crabs of the world |author=Peter K. L. Ng, Danièle Guinot & Peter J. F. Davie |url=http://rmbr.nus.edu.sg/rbz/biblio/s17/s17rbz.pdf |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110606061453/http://rmbr.nus.edu.sg/rbz/biblio/s17/s17rbz.pdf |archivedate=2011-06-06 |access-date=2013-04-23 }}</ref>
*''[[Bathypluma_chuni|Bathypluma chuni]]'' <small>(Doflein, 1904)</small>
*''[[Bathypluma_forficula|Bathypluma forficula]]'' <small>De Saint Laurent, 1989</small>
*''[[Bathypluma_spinifer|Bathypluma spinifer]]'' <small>De Saint Laurent, 1989</small>
*''[[Retropluma_denticulata|Retropluma denticulata]]'' <small>Rathbun, 1932</small>
*''[[Retropluma_quadrata|Retropluma quadrata]]'' <small>De Saint Laurent, 1989</small>
*''[[Retropluma_notopus|Retropluma notopus]]'' <small>(Alcock & Anderson, 1894)</small>
*''[[Retropluma_planiforma|Retropluma planiforma]]'' <small>Kensley, 1969</small>
*''[[Retropluma_plumosa|Retropluma plumosa]]'' <small>Tesch, 1918</small>
*''[[Retropluma_serenei|Retropluma serenei]]'' <small>De Saint Laurent, 1989</small>
*''[[Retropluma_solomonensis|Retropluma solomonensis]]'' <small>McLay, 2006</small>

該科的化石發現於[[白堊紀晚期|白堊紀晚期]]之後，最早的[[化石|化石]]包括在[[加利福尼亞|加利福尼亞]][[科尼亞克階|科尼亞克階]]-[[麥斯里希特階|麥斯里希特階]]發現的''Archaeopus antennatus''，和在[[日本|日本]][[土侖階|土侖階]]-麥斯特里希特階發現的''Archaeopus ezoensis''。<ref>{{cite journal |title=New Cretaceous and Tertiary decapod crustaceans from western North America |author=Carrie E. Schweitzer & Rodney M. Feldmann |journal=[[Bulletin_of_the_Mizunami_Fossil_Museum|Bulletin of the Mizunami Fossil Museum]] |volume=28 |year=2001 |pages=173–210 |url=http://www.city.mizunami.gifu.jp/odocs/sightseeing/mizunami/cultural_property/institution/Bull28/BMFM28-173-210(13MB).pdf |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120305164854/http://www.city.mizunami.gifu.jp/odocs/sightseeing/mizunami/cultural_property/institution/Bull28/BMFM28-173-210(13MB).pdf |archivedate=2012-03-05 |access-date=2013-04-19 }}</ref>

